    "summary": "All-round coverage banker from The Netherlands with 15+ years of experience in wholesale and commercial banking | Special focus on global corporate and investment banking solutions (loan syndication, private debt, club deals, bilateral loans, M&A) and project financing of large infrastructure and renewable energy projects | Master of Science degree in Business Administration.\n\nKeywords:\nOrigination and client coverage, structured finance, dealmaker, bridge between East and West, intrinsic curiosity.\n\n\nDeal experience (highlights):\n\n* Participated in a US$790.0 million secured syndicated loan facility for a listed corporate client in the international transportation industry (ticket size US$80.0 million);\n\n* Participated in a \u20ac1.0 billion unsecured syndicated loan facility for a hyperscale data center joint venture across Europe (ticket size \u20ac50.0 million);\n\n* Involved in the structuring and coordination of a \u20ac12.7 billion M&A transaction of a Pan-European logistics real estate portfolio (underwriting share of \u20ac3.0 billion);\n\n* Involved in the restructuring of a \u20ac100.0 million privately placed term loan facility for a large automotive supplier operating in Europe, Asia Pacific and the Americas (ticket size \u20ac18.5 million);\n\n* Arranged a bilateral term loan facility for a management buy-in (MBI) and expansion financing in the Dutch and German leisure industry;\n\n* Arranged acquisition financing for a fast-growing tech company in Singapore and a developer of online gaming/advertising platforms in Istanbul, Turkey;\n\n* Arranged an investment loan transaction for a reputable private hospitality group in Amsterdam, The Netherlands;\n\n* Participated in a US$200.0 million promissory note facility (SSD) for a listed global distributor of speciality chemicals and food ingredients (ticket size US$30.0 million);\n\n* Participated in a \u20ac170.0 million promissory note facility (SSD) for a renowned European equipment rental company (ticket size \u20ac15.0 million);\n\n* Onboarded a global leading commercial aircraft lessor and successfully set up multiple term deposits on a 3/6m roll-over basis (average outstanding balance US$30.0 million).\n\n* Managing various project financings of large public infrastructure and renewable energy projects (investments from \u20ac15.0 million to a few hundred million euros).",
